\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dot{u}=k_{1}\dot{e}+\ddot{x}_{d}-\Psi\left(\kappa,\widehat{\theta}\right)+\beta\text{sgn}\left(e\right)+e+k_{2}r
\]

